snippet: The winners of the national challenge had been asked to come up with original recipes that were affordable, delicious and met nutritional guidelines.
abstract: Healthy Lunchtime Challenge, created by Cooking Up Big Dreams chief executive Tanya Steel, invites young chefs to enter healthy recipe contest and rewards winners with White House dinner featuring their recipes.
lead_paragraph: The winners of the national challenge had been asked to come up with original recipes that were affordable, delicious and met nutritional guidelines.

headline.main: White House Lunch Features Healthy Recipes by Young Chefs
